OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAberfan: Tests on children 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fafter disaster 'like       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftorture'                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some of the children who survived the  
OL,6, Aberfan disaster have said they were   
OL,7, put through distressing medical tests, 
OL,8, which one described as "torture".      
OL,10,FIn 1966, 116 children and 28 adults    
OL,11,Fwere killed when coal waste slid down a
OL,12,Fhillside, burying a primary school and 
OL,13,Fhomes in the Merthyr Tydfil village.   
OL,15,FSome survivors said they endured more  
OL,16,Ftorment in order to establish how much 
OL,17,Fcompensation families should get.      
OL,19,F"That film Frankenstein is exactly what
OL,20,Fhappened to us," Gaynor Madgwick said. 
